  "title": "Assistant Accounts Manager",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilitie:</p><ul><li>Preparing and maintaining financial reports, ensuring compliance of all filing requirements for audit, GST and corporate tax purposes,</li><li>Preparation and closing of monthly and annual financial statements, all accounting processes and tasks such as AP & AR process, GL, petty cash, account reconciliation, and GST,</li><li>Coordination of accounts of our Hong Kong’s office and offices in other regions,</li><li>Coordinate and liaise with internal departments parties to support intercompany activities and in the management of grants,</li><li>Daily monitoring of the financial aspect of the company,</li><li>Support forecasting and budgeting exercises per corporate guidelines,</li><li>Assist in new computerisation / digital processes and system implementation when required,</li><li>To recommend financial actions by analyzing accounting options,</li><li>Assist to train and guide new accounting clerical staff,</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p></p>",
